---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Impressum / Legal Notice — LunarTrust"
  description="Legal notice and provider identification for LunarTrust per § 5 TMG."
>
  <article class="impressum">
    <header class="impressum-header">
      <h1>Impressum <span class="title-divider">/</span> Legal Notice</h1>
      <nav class="lang-nav" aria-label="Jump to language version">
        <a href="#en">English</a>
        <span aria-hidden="true">·</span>
        <a href="#de">Deutsch</a>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <!-- ── English ─────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
    <section class="lang-block" id="en">
      <div class="lang-badge">English</div>
      <p class="legal-note">
        Required information pursuant to § 5 TMG (German Telemedia Act)
      </p>

      <section>
        <h2>Responsible for content</h2>
        <div class="contact-details"
             aria-label="Abdallah Ben-Salah, Edwin-Scharff-Ring 58, 22309 Hamburg, Germany">
          <span class="addr" aria-hidden="true" data-a="Abdallah" data-b=" Ben-Salah"></span><br aria-hidden="true" />
          <span class="addr" aria-hidden="true" data-a="Edwin-Scharff-Ring" data-b=" 58"></span><br aria-hidden="true" />
          <span class="addr" aria-hidden="true" data-a="22309" data-b=" Hamburg"></span><br aria-hidden="true" />
          <span class="addr" aria-hidden="true" data-a="Germany" data-b=""></span>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p class="contact-details">
          Email: <a href="mailto:ab.bensalah@pm.me">ab.bensalah@pm.me</a>
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>About this website</h2>
        <p>
          LunarTrust is a private, non-commercial project. The website is
          operated without commercial intent.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Liability for content</h2>
        <p>
          The content of this website has been created with the greatest
          possible care. No guarantee is given for the accuracy, completeness,
          or timeliness of the content. As a private provider I am responsible
          for my own content on these pages in accordance with general law (§ 7
          para. 1 TMG). Under §§ 8–10 TMG, however, I am not obliged to monitor
          transmitted or stored third-party information.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Liability for links</h2>
        <p>
          This website contains links to external third-party websites over
          whose content I have no influence. The respective provider or operator
          of the linked pages is always responsible for their content. Permanent
          monitoring of linked pages without concrete evidence of a legal
          violation is unreasonable. Links will be removed promptly upon
          becoming aware of any infringement.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Copyright</h2>
        <p>
          The content and works created by the site operator on this website are
          subject to German copyright law. Reproduction, editing, distribution,
          and any kind of use beyond the limits of copyright law require the
          written consent of the author. Downloads and copies of this site are
          permitted only for private, non-commercial use. The source code of
          this website is available on GitHub under the MIT licence. This
          licence applies to the code only, not to texts, logos, or other
          content.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Dispute resolution</h2>
        <p>
          The European Commission provides a platform for online dispute
          resolution (ODR):
          <a
            href="https://ec.europa.eu/consumers/odr"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            ec.europa.eu/consumers/odr ↗
          </a>. I am neither willing nor obliged to participate in dispute
          resolution proceedings before a consumer arbitration board.
        </p>
      </section>
    </section>

    <hr class="lang-divider" />

    <!-- ── Deutsch ─────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
    <section class="lang-block" id="de">
      <div class="lang-badge">Deutsch</div>
      <p class="legal-note">Pflichtangaben gemäß § 5 TMG</p>

      <section>
        <h2>Verantwortlich für den Inhalt</h2>
        <div class="contact-details"
             aria-label="Abdallah Ben-Salah, Edwin-Scharff-Ring 58, 22309 Hamburg, Deutschland">
          <span class="addr" aria-hidden="true" data-a="Abdallah" data-b=" Ben-Salah"></span><br aria-hidden="true" />
          <span class="addr" aria-hidden="true" data-a="Edwin-Scharff-Ring" data-b=" 58"></span><br aria-hidden="true" />
          <span class="addr" aria-hidden="true" data-a="22309" data-b=" Hamburg"></span><br aria-hidden="true" />
          <span class="addr" aria-hidden="true" data-a="Deutschland" data-b=""></span>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Kontakt</h2>
        <p class="contact-details">
          E-Mail: <a href="mailto:ab.bensalah@pm.me">ab.bensalah@pm.me</a>
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Hinweis zur Website</h2>
        <p>
          LunarTrust ist ein privates, nicht-kommerzielles Projekt. Die Website
          wird ohne wirtschaftliche Absicht betrieben.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Haftung für Inhalte</h2>
        <p>
          Die Inhalte dieser Website wurden mit größtmöglicher Sorgfalt
          erstellt. Für die Richtigkeit, Vollständigkeit und Aktualität der
